e, with medium stopping power.','45','575 RPM','50','34','205'),(32,'Mk17 CQB','7.62x51mm caliber assault rifle, adapted for close quarter operations, high damage and severe recoil.','40','585 RPM','50','20','161'),(33,'SR-25','Highly customizable semi-automatic rifle. Effective from long to medium range.','61','Semi-automatic','38','20','101'),(34,'MPX','Close to mid-range 9mm submachine gun, medium to high penetration.','26','830 RPM','50','30','181'),(35,'SPAS-12','Lightweight customizable 12-gauge semi-automatic shotgun.','35','Semi-automatic','50','7','36'),(36,'PARA-308','BOPE PARA-308 is a more compact version of the battle proven FAL with high stopping power.','48','650 RPM','50','30','241'),(37,'M249','Iconic LMG, accurate in medium range with high ammo capacity and efficient suppressive fire.','48','650 RPM','50','100','401'),(38,'M12','	Close to mid-range 9mm submachine gun with low recoil and a medium fire rate. Favored by BOPE.','40','550 RPM','50','30','181'),(39,'SPAS-15','Magazine-fed, semi-automatic shotgun, bringing a modern twist on the SPAS-12.','30','Semi-automatic','50','6','37');
