INSERT INTO `UniquneGadget` VALUES (1,'The Caber','The Breaching Hammer is capable of making doors in destructible walls and instantly destroying barricades. Additionally, the Breaching Hammer can be used as a melee weapon and to destroy barbed wire.'),(2,'EG MKO-EMP Grenade','Throwable Electromagnetic Pulse grenade capable of disabling most hostile electronics within a short radius, even through walls. Disabling hostile cameras for 10 seconds instead.'),(3,'Compound Z8','Throwable canister containing a toxic gas. Sticks to any surface and can be remotely detonated at will.'),(4,'GC90 Signal Disrupter','The GC90 “Moni”, blocks the signal from a remote detonator or control from reaching any device within range.'),(5,'M120 CREM','Modified grenade launcher capable of containing a single 40mm breaching round. Detonating shortly after impact.'),(6,'Brimstone BC-3','Rolling mat affixed to an incendiary device that can be remotely detonated. Capable of breaching reinforced walls.'),(7,'UTP1 Tactical Panel','Rollable armor panel made of Polyethylene, ballistic fabric, and boron ceramic micro plates.'),(8,'HB-5 Cardiac Sensor','This heartbeat detector can read thermal signatures through walls and other obstacles.'),(9,'\"Le Roc\" Shield','Made from a composite of reinforced alloys and Kevlar, \"Le Roc\" is capable of collapsing into half its size, allowing for increased mobility to its wielder.'),(10,'RSD Model 1','Bulkier, slower and more silent than the standard observation drone, the shock drone, it\'s capable of destroying electronic equipment as well as most electronic gadgets.'),(11,'MPD-0 Stim Pistol','Handheld, trigger operated pistol powered by a pressurized CO2 canister. Contains a 1mg dose of epinephrine, in a saline solution.'),(12,'R1N \"Rhino\" Armor','A multi-hit boron ceramic plate with a special spall-stop coating, and a back-face deformation (BFD) plate stored in a light weight sturdy satchel for rapid field deployment.'),(13,'HDS Flip Sight','Mounted on a hinge allowing it to flip into position, the HDS Flip Sight provides the wielder access to an unmatched level of zoom as well as the ability to see through smoke.'),(14,'APM-6 \"Matryoshka\"','Featuring a piston that burrows through unreinforced walls, floors and even armor panels with ease, the \'Matryoshka\', when anchored, shoots live cluster grenades.'),(15,'EDD MK II','C4 charge that may be mounted into windows and door frames.'),(16,'Shumikha Launcher','Area denial heavy incendiary grenade launcher can bounce multiple times, and their fuse timer only starts after the first bounce, giving them a lot of versatility.'),(17,'G52-Tactical Shield','Ballistic shield light enough to permit its wielder to sprint, it comes equipped with 24 flash-bang grenades spread over 3 rows providing a high intensity light source when triggered.'),(18,'Red MKIII \"Spectre\"','Wrist mounted mobile phone-sized sensor capable of detecting electronic gadgets and equipment within its range.'),(19,'ADS-MK IV \"Magpie\"','Full range grenade launcher mountable on walls and floors featuring four surveillance cameras allowing for precise targeting of hostile equipment.'),(20,'CED-1','The CED-1 features an taser wired to a car battery enclosed in a copper cage with jumper cables. It\'s defensive purpose is to destroy any gadget it comes in contact with making it a viable counter to exo-thermic charges and X-KAIROS pallets. Placeable on any metallic surface, it can protect barbed wire, deployable shields, and reinforced walls.'),(21,'SK 4-12 (Skeleton Key)','Under-barrel mounted 12 gauge shotgun with four round capacity, used in tandem with an assault rifle. The Skeleton Key allows the operator to alternate between their standard issue assault rifle and a breaching shotgun with ease and efficiency.'),(22,'Sterling MK2 LHT','Requiring two people to release the jaws and reset the trap. The rubber mat and concealed metal jaws are bolted in place. When the pressure plate is engaged, two sets of jaws at ankle and shin height deploy, locking the person in place.'),(23,'MK 0 Rifle Shield','Created with multiple layers of transparent polycarbonate and thermoplastic armor, coated with a spall shield and backed with ultra-light weight laminated glass. The TARS MK 0 Rifle Shield protects the user against blunt impact and artillery fire.'),(24,'Gyro Cam MK2','Encased in a tinted silicone ball, coated in micro-suction cups, the MK2 maintains a clear view thanks to the internal gyroscope that dictates the angle of the lens. The suction cups allow the camera to adhere to any surface, while the gyroscope mounted lens stabilises the camera angle and focus. The live video feed is available to all operators.'),(25,'TAC MK0 Tactical Crossbow','Use a glass bolt to deliver a swift and silent assault against hostiles without alerting them to your position. The glass cartridge breaks on impact releasing a gas that ignites the oxygen in the surrounding area. Deliver swift and agile assaults without alerting your opponents of your position.'),(26,'Luison','The Luison is wrapped in a rock-based mineral fiber to both insulate and soundproof the silencer. This weapon allows Caveira to incapacitate her target discreetly and conduct an interrogation. It\'s is not only formidable to neutralize your opponent while remaining undetected; it also ensures that no one gets away.');
